William Kendis https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/William_Kendis 0 William Kendis (May 27, 1916 – December 17, 1980) was an American actor. Kendis appeared in television series' including an appearance as murder victim Walter Prescott in the Perry Mason episode, "The Case of the Lame Canary." He also appeared on The Twilight Zone, Bewitched, 77 Sunset Strip, Family Affair and The Flying Nun. He was born in New Hampshire and died in Los Angeles, California.
